+    package="edu.hzuapps.androidlabs">

+    <application
+        android:allowBackup="true"
+        android:icon="@mipmap/ic_launcher"
+        android:label="@string/app_name"
+        android:supportsRtl="true"
+        android:theme="@style/AppTheme">
+        <activity android:name=".homworks.net1414080903137.Net1414080903137Activity">
+            <intent-filter>
+                <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
+
+                <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
+            </intent-filter>
+        </activity>
+        <activity android:name=".homworks.net1414080903137.Net1414080903137SecondActivity" />
+        <activity
+            android:name=".homworks.net1414080903137.Net1414080903137ThirdActivity"
+            android:label="@string/title_activity_thrid"
+            android:theme="@style/AppTheme.NoActionBar" />
+        <activity android:name=".homworks.net1414080903137.Net1414080903137FourthActivity" />
+        <activity android:name=".homworks.net1414080903137.Net1414080903137fFifthActivity"></activity>
+    </application>
+
+</manifest>
